Enum SwipeDismissList.UndoMode

    public static enum SwipeDismissList.UndoMode
extends java.lang.Enum<SwipeDismissList.UndoMode>
    Defines the mode a SwipeDismissList handles multiple undos.

    • Enum Constant Summary

      Enum Constants 
      Enum Constant and Description
      COLLAPSED_UNDO
      Give the user the possibility to undo multiple deletions all together.
      MULTI_UNDO
      Give the user the possibility to undo multiple deletions one by one.
      SINGLE_UNDO
      Only give the user the possibility to undo the last action.

    • Enum Constant Detail

      • SINGLE_UNDO

        public static final SwipeDismissList.UndoMode SINGLE_UNDO
        Only give the user the possibility to undo the last action. As soon as another item is deleted, there is no chance to undo the previous deletion.

      • MULTI_UNDO

        public static final SwipeDismissList.UndoMode MULTI_UNDO
        Give the user the possibility to undo multiple deletions one by one. Every click on Undo will undo the previous deleted item. Undos will be collected as long as the undo popup stays open. As soon as the popup vanished (because autoHideDelay is over) all saved undos will be discarded.

      • COLLAPSED_UNDO

        public static final SwipeDismissList.UndoMode COLLAPSED_UNDO
        Give the user the possibility to undo multiple deletions all together. As long as the popup stays open all further deletions will be collected. A click on the undo button will undo ALL deletions saved. As soon as the popup vanished (because autoHideDelay is over) all saved undos will be discarded.
